sentence: how high is the highest point in the largest state ?
sentence-with-vars: how high is the highest point in the largest state ?
sql: select highlow.highest_elevation from highlow , state where highlow.state_name = state.state_name and state.area = ( select max ( state.area ) from state ) ;
sql-with-vars: select highlow.highest_elevation from highlow , state where highlow.state_name = state.state_name and state.area = ( select max ( state.area ) from state ) ;
